<abstract><t>This contribution addresses the service providers' requirements to support VPN-Oriented data center services. It describes the characteristics and the framework of VPN-oriented data center services and specifies the requirements on how to maintain and manage the virtual resources within data center resources and the supporting network infrastructures for those services.</t></abstract>

